This paper is about personalized explanation in machine learning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the importance of making machine learning models understandable to humans, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the collection and use of personal data, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and privacy (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the properties of explanations that can be personalized, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG).
